    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "blk_notionroot",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Hendricks Residence \u2014 master bath install day one: Aria Stone slab AS-19842 arrived 10/21 8 AM. Cut with diamond blade, no chipping. Rebecca on site 11 AM, thrilled with the vein pattern.",
    "order": "1",
    "created_time": "2026-10-05T12:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-15T12:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185400065",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "blk_notionroot",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Martin Condo \u2014 Circa Bardot pair for entry, approved by Sarah. Trade $8,400 all-in. Order placed via trade portal 10/5.",
    "order": "2",
    "created_time": "2026-10-05T12:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-15T12:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185400066",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "blk_notionroot",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Desert Vista \u2014 Model A walnut console delivery Wed 10/21 morning. Fabric memo binder locked with all 3 model palettes.",
    "order": "3",
    "created_time": "2026-10-05T12:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-15T12:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185400067",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "blk_notionroot",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "Spec home \u2014 wine wall walnut + brass installed 11/30. Kevin's listing agent scheduled walkthrough 12/1.",
    "order": "4",
    "created_time": "2026-10-05T12:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-15T12:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
  {
    "id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185400068",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "blk_notionroot",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "ASID Arizona chapter meeting 11/9 6:30 PM at HQ. RSVPd for Natalie, Sophie, and me. Design leadership panel + Q4 chapter updates.",
    "order": "5",
    "created_time": "2026-10-05T12:00:00+00:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-15T12:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": "false"
  },
